item.description:
Looking for something to do Friday night?
Want to wish the Doc farewell before his sabbatical?

The Doc will be off training the Jr. Doc LateNite shortly, so this will likely be his last meetup for a few months (or longer if Mrs LateNite has a say in it...)

So whether you are looking for some fun on Friday or wish to give the Doc some advice on Jr, it'll be a fun time for all.

We'll start at Spats on college hill and will stay in that area throughout the night. The group will stay at Spats until 9:30pm, so if you will be later than that send the Doc an email.

Spats on Angell, the Doc'll see ya there.

-doc

item.name: Doc's calm before the storm send off
